('DevOps最佳实践指南', '如何建立高效的DevOps团队和流程', '<h2>DevOps最佳实践</h2><p>DevOps是提升开发效率的关键，本文介绍如何建立高效的DevOps团队和流程。</p>', '软件', 'DevOps', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1461749280684-dccba630e2f6?w=800&h=400&fit=crop', 876, 36, 0, '2026-05-08 12:00:00', NOW(), NOW(), 'https://example.com/devops-best-practices');
